{"tid":1345908,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組一定要對外寫「恐襲」","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:23:10.000Z","uid":153938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5577d5275f2d982dbbd08c8b8ae0a81aa574fff7","tid":1345908,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"梁啓智：香港政府亂來，612就叫「暴動」，721就叫「衝突」。不，昨晚在元朗發生的是有組織有預謀、持續發生、針對平民百姓並以製造恐慌為目的的無差別襲擊。它就是恐襲。我們要一齊清楚講明，昨晚在元朗發生的是一場恐襲。<br />\n香港法例第575章《聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)條例》規定，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「作出或恐嚇作出行動」，懷有「危害作出該行動的人以外的人的生命」的意圖，就是恐怖主義行為。</span></span>昨晚現場施害者所說的「</span>唔係白衫就打」，完全符合這個定義。所以，說這些人是暴徒還是過輕了。他們是恐怖分子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@leungkaichihk/%E8%AC%9B%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E6%98%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2-c484259a646a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40leungkaichihk%2F%25E8%25AC%259B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25A5%259A-%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2-c484259a646a&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqZAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=35fe452f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@leungkaichihk/%E8%AC%9B%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E6%98%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2-c484259a646a</a>"},{"pid":"d9351f2eeda003295c17d1af4dd0efa800d8be29","tid":1345908,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38e0fa98f484afc626d70df6dd8c1d2ae9d0948c","tid":1345908,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講。"},{"pid":"18d8c015ddc18ca9b57d998cb7f391ed35ef5186","tid":1345908,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"向Law Society投訴何君堯條